SELECT DISTINCT name, occurred_at
FROM accounts
JOIN orders ON accounts.id = orders.account_id
WHERE occurred_at >= '2016-01-02';
sql
Copy code
SELECT DISTINCT name, occurred_at
FROM accounts
JOIN orders ON accounts.id = orders.account_id
WHERE occurred_at BETWEEN '2014-01-01' AND '2015-01-01';
Description:
Extracts unique account names and order dates within specific date ranges.

SELECT DISTINCT name, occurred_at
FROM accounts
JOIN orders ON accounts.id = orders.account_id
WHERE occurred_at >= (
	SELECT MAX(occurred_at) FROM orders
) - INTERVAL '1 year';
Description:
Finds all accounts that placed orders within the last year of the dataset.
